Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,独特の世界観もっとる奴ですわ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.48,def2,....GOU....,0,0,0,,Is he fast ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:15.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,速いか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.18,def2,...KUBO....,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:17.75,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そらもう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:22.50,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのハチロクのドライバーにはあいつがついている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:22.45,def2,....GOU....,0,0,0,,That Eight-Six driver is\Nbacked by a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:26.42,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,高橋涼介がな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:27.51,def2,....GOU....,0,0,0,,Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.43,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この間から気にしてるようでっけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:33.40,def2,...KUBO....,0,0,0,,You look like you've been troubled by him.\NDo you have some kind of issue with him ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:33.42,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何ぞ因縁でもあるんでっか　そのー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.13,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,高橋涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.50,def2,....GOU....,0,0,0,,Takahashi Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.13,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.30,def2,....GOU....,0,0,0,,I do. No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:51.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 俺じゃなくて　もっと因縁のある奴がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.93,def2,....GOU....,0,0,0,,There's someone else \Nwho does more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:57.25,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,NB8CロードスターとAE86トレノ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:58.42,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,NB8C Roadster and AE86 Trueno...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:04.25,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,...both have a light and compact body\Nwith a small displacement NA engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:06:03.35,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,共に軽量コンパクトな車体に小排気量NAエンジンを搭載し
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:07.79,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,軽快なフットワークを身上にワインディングロードを疾走する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:07.96,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,{keikai}They take advantage of their\Nagility to zip along a winding road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのコンセプトは共通だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.03,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,They share the same concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,生まれた年代は異なるが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:17.25,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,Even though they were made years\Napart, their potential is very similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:17.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,クルマのポテンシャルは限りなく接近したものになっている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.11,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:23.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,故に勝敗はそれぞれのドライバーの感性に委ねられる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:23.64,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,{shohai}...victory will be decided by the driver's instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:45.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大宮智史というNB乗りの感性と藤原拓海というハチロク乗りの感性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:35.11,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,The instincts of the NB driver,\NOmiya Satoshi, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:45.69,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,...the instincts of the Eight-Six\Ndriver, Fujiwara Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どちらがよりクルマとの感性が合っているか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:52.40,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,I think the result will be determined by\Nwhose instincts match their car the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:52.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝負はそれが結果を分ける気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:56.42,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで生き物みたいだな　二人が乗っているクルマは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:57.33,def2,.FUMIHIRO..,0,0,0,,You make it sound\Nlike both cars are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:02.28,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうかもしれないな　クルマからの一瞬の声を聞き逃した方が負ける
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.47,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:02.56,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,The one who doesn't listen to the voice\Nof their car, even for a moment, will lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:19.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,北関東エリアを負けなしで駆け抜けてきた伝説のチーム　プロジェクトDとは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:20.90,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Project D is a legendary team which swept\Nthe northern Kanto area without any losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな走りなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:24.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせなら　それを後追いでじっくり見てみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:27.00,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{douse}{\c&HFFFFFF&}It'd be wise to carefully observe how they drive from behind. That's what Kobayakawa thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:26.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小早川はそう考えた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:29.98,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にも同じ気持ちはある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.94,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{ore}I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だけどそこに落とし穴があった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.65,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}But that was the pitfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:38.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相手を見るということは自分のペースを守れていないということなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:38.25,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}To observe your opponent\Nmeans you can't keep your pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:44.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのハチロクを見ていくのは危険だ　そんな気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:45.06,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I sense it's risky to\Njust watch the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:47.47,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これは俺の勘だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.00,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{korewa}I just have a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だから俺は先行で行く
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.65,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That's why I chose the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:57.00,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'll keep my pace without\Nany obstacles ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:56.94,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,目前には何もない状況で自分のペースを作る
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:00.61,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つためにだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.70,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...in order to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:14.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ダウンヒルはどうなりますかね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.65,def2,....MAN....,0,0,0,,I wonder how the downhill will develop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:17.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,簡単には勝たせてもらえないだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:18.27,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,I don't think we can win very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:20.87,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶっちゃけレベル高いよ　ここの連中は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:21.76,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,To be honest, our opponents' level is very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:27.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にしたって結果から見るほど楽な勝負じゃなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:27.50,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,My race wasn't easy, even though it \Nmay have looked like it from the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:31.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,特に今　藤原が相手にしてる奴は手強いぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:32.03,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,That guy Fujiwara's facing is especially tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:36.63,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,公道ランナーとしてはほとんど完成の域に達してる奴だろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.50,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,He must have perfected street driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことが分かるんっすか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.84,def2,...KENTA...,0,0,0,,Can you tell ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:43.23,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,I can sense it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺には分かるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:47.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,藤原も　それは感じてるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.50,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...and Fujiwara...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.82,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...senses it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:56.98,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,隙がない　空間の全てが埋め尽くされてる感じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:57.25,def2,..TAKUMI...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The entire space seems filled,\Nas if he's always on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:11.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先行するNBがタメにタメて　どっかでスパートを駆けてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:12.25,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,The leading NB will hold on, then it \Nwill suddenly accelerate somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コースを知り尽くしてるだけに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:17.40,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,As a local who knows this course best, he can\Nmaintain his pace, which gives him an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:17.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ペースを握れる先行は地元にとっては有利なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ってことは　勝負所は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:20.04,def2,...KENTA...,0,0,0,,So the decisive point will be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:24.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,終盤の勾配がきつく　路面の荒れた区間だろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:25.76,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,The steep, rough road \Nnear the end of the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:30.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サスペンションの基本設計が古いハチロクにとっては不利な区間ですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:30.50,def2,....MAN....,0,0,0,,That section is disadvantageous to the\NEight-Six because its suspension design is old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:34.86,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁ　そういうことになるな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.72,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:38.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど不利なのは今に始まったことじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:39.30,def2,KEISUKEBUT,0,0,0,,But our disadvantage \Ndidn't just begin tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:43.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,敢えて敵地で戦うのはレッドサンズ時代からの俺達のテーマだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:44.06,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,It's been our motto to fight on our \Nopponents' stage since the Red Suns days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:44.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.50,def2,...KENTA...,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:50.39,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アニキが練り上げたアウェイで戦いのノウハウはいつも完璧に機能する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:51.04,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,My brother's carefully built know-how of fighting\Nthose away races has always worked perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,向こうがコースに特化したスペシャリストなら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:57.00,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,If our opponent is a \Nspecialist on this course...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:01.71,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちは敵地攻略に特化したスペシャルチームだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:01.93,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,...we're a special team organized\Nto attack enemy territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:06.21,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちのスピードが最終的には相手を上回るのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:07.43,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,Whoever is faster than the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:09.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それが結果的には全てだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:09.40,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,That will be everything in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:18.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,高橋涼介という天才がいる限り　プロジェクトDに不可能はない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:19.04,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Nothing is impossible for Project D, as long\Nas we have the genius of Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:21.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はそう思ってるけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:21.80,def2,..KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I truly believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:31.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,近いぞ　もうすぐそこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:31.92,def2,....MAN....,0,0,0,,They're close, almost at the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,中間地点のヘアピンに突っ込んでくるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.97,def2,....MAN....,0,0,0,,They're gonna dive into the mid-section hairpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:38.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,来たぁ！　オーシ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:37.65,def2,....MAN....,0,0,0,,There they are !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.60,def2,....MAN....,0,0,0,,Alright !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,行っけー　大宮　本気出せー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:52.06,def2,....MAN....,0,0,0,,Go, Omiya !\NThrow everything you've got at 'em !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ハチロクなんかぶっちぎれー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:53.67,def2,....MAN....,0,0,0,,Leave the Eight-Six in the dust !
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:03.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ピタリとついたまま中間地点を通過していった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:04.00,def2,KOBAYAKAWA.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}They've passed the mid-section, fighting tail to nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:05.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまでは同じ展開だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.80,def2,KOBAYAKAWA.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's developed the same\Nway up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:12.79,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どこかで必ずスパートを駆けてくるのは　分かってたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:13.07,def2,KOBAYAKAWA.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I knew my opponent would \Naccelerate somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:23.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,来る来ると思いながら　なかなか来ない相手に俺はじれていった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:23.76,def2,KOBAYAKAWA.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I was frustrated by my opponent, who didn't\Nmake his move according to my predictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:29.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜだか　ひどく追い詰められた気持ちになっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:29.00,def2,KOBAYAKAWA.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}For some reason, I felt cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:38.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同じことはあのハチロクのドライバーにも起こっているんじゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:39.00,def2,KOBAYAKAWA.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The same thing must be\Nhappening to that Eight-Six driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:40.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これは大宮のペースだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:43.40,def2,KOBAYAKAWA.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{korewa}In a situation where Omiya maintains his pace,\Nneither of them can ease up, even for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:43.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一瞬たりとも　気が抜けない状況が続く
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:05.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まだまだ半分終わったばかりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.09,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}We're only at the halfway point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,テンションは目一杯振り切れそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:11.35,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}My tension is almost going off the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　俺にはもう一段階ある
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:14.68,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}But I have one more level.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:20.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その闘争心のスイッチが切り替わる瞬間がどこかで来る
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:20.40,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}There will be a moment when\Nmy fighting spirit turns on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:13:00.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,前よりも足太くなった気がするな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:00.95,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Seems like my legs got thicker...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:03.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この辺とか この辺とか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:03.15,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Here...and here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.71,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,筋トレやってるからかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:08.01,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It must be because of the muscle training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:10.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ドライバーの飛距離が伸びるのはいいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:10.56,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I can hit my drives farther, which is nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:13.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,パンツのサイズ変わるのは微妙だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.98,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...but my pants size changed, which isn't so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夏休みだしな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:20.23,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm supposed to be on summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:22.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,たまには海とか行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.50,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I wish I could go to the beach once in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,拓海君とか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:28.28,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...with Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも無理か忙しいから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.02,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That's impossible. I'm too busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:42.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,拓海君は今頃神奈川でレースなんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:42.59,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Takumi must be racing in Kanagawa now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.21,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一度見てみたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:47.52,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I want to see him race just once, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:50.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見たらきっと 凄く強いんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:50.57,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...that'll probably scare the hell out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:55.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張ってね　拓海君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.94,def2,...MIKA....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Do your best, Takumi.\NMake sure you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:57.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対勝ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:06.21,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.58,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Good, I'm focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:07.61,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,集中している
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:22.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コースの攻略という観点から言えば
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:27.64,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,From a strategic point of view, I think\Nbraking is the most important on the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:27.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ダウンヒルで一番重要なのは ブレーキングだと俺は思っている
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:29.87,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,平坦地に比べて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:35.15,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,{heitan}Stopping distance increases dramatically on the downhill\Nversus level ground, so one braking mistake is critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,制動距離が飛躍的に伸びる下りでは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:35.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブレーキングのミスは命取りになるし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:40.63,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サーキットのように距離を示してくれる看板のない真っ黒な公道で
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:41.04,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,{circuit}Unlike circuits, public streets are dark without\Nany distance markers before each corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:43.75,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,正確にブレーキングポイントを設定するには
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.80,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,{seikaku}So, to determine the precise braking point...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,研ぎ澄まされた感覚だけが頼りなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:51.24,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,{togisumasareta}...you can only rely on your refined intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:54.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,目印は役に立たない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.41,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,{mejirushi}Landmarks are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:08.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,人間の脳の持っている潜在能力というのは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:10.55,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,I'm constantly surprised by the\Npotential of the human brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.63,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,つくづく凄いと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:14.58,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,藤原特別に　ブレーキングの感覚が優れている
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:14.50,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,Fujiwara's braking sense is exceptional.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:19.75,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,走り慣れた地元のドライバを相手にして
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:23.78,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,That's why he can keep winning on the downhill\Nagainst locals who are familiar with their course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:23.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ダウンヒルで勝ち続きられるのはそのセンスのおかげなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:27.63,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,練習だけで身につくものじゃないよな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:28.20,def2,.FUMIHIRO..,0,0,0,,It's not something you can \Nacquire by just practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:30.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,間違いなく天性の物でしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:30.90,def2,.MATSUMOTO.,0,0,0,,He's definitely a natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.29,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,テールツーノーズで後ろから追うかけながら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:38.40,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,You can figure out your opponent's driving skills by\Nwatching how he brakes as you stay right on his tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:35.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブレーキングを見ていれば
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.63,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相手のドライバの実力はすぐに分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:41.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにな 難しいことじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:42.16,def2,.FUMIHIRO..,0,0,0,,You're right. That's not so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:44.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,実力が拮抗してればなお更でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:45.30,def2,.MATSUMOTO.,0,0,0,,And it's even more true between\Ntwo drivers with similar skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:48.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に言えば 見せないことは駆け引きにもなる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:49.26,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,Conversely, hiding skills can be the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:51.50,def2,.RYOSUKE:..,0,0,0,, You show your true braking skills when...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:51.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本気のブレーキングを見せる時は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:57.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負に行くときだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:56.84,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,...you decide to settle the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,遅れた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:23.15,def2,..TAKUMI...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I was late, only a little, but definitely late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:23.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんの少しだけど 確実に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:30.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先のロングストレートからハートブレーキング
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.93,def2,..TAKUMI...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That hard braking from the long straightaway...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:34.50,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,たった一回切りだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:36.28,def2,..TAKUMI...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Even if it was just that one time,\N{only for once, but} I was late in braking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブレーキングで遅れた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:41.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,スゲー　突っ込み
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:41.31,def2,....MAN....,0,0,0,,Incredible entry !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.50,def2,....MAN....,0,0,0,,The gap with the Eight-Six is getting wider !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ハチロクとの差が開き始めてるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,百パーセントガチンコのモードで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:52.40,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm using everything\N I've got at 100% capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:54.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,デンジャラスゾーンに突入だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:54.39,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm in a dangerous zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,きてまっせ すぐそこまで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.40,def2,...KUBO....,0,0,0,,They're getting closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:02.82,def2,...KUBO....,0,0,0,,They're almost at the corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:26.30,def2,...KUBO....,0,0,0,,Looks quite dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:25.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見るからに危なげな動きに見えますけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:30.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時代の車は足を固めていくと あいう挙動になるんですわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:31.63,def2,...KUBO....,0,0,0,,The cars of that era tend to behave like\Nthat when their suspension is stiffened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:34.01,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ハチロクらしいと言えばらしいんやけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.65,def2,...KUBO....,0,0,0,,You can say it's very 86-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.75,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは平均スピード百キロ以下のステージ限定で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:41.49,def2,...KUBO....,0,0,0,,{are}The car's seriously tuned to be the very best in the stages \Nwhere the average speed is below 100km/h (62mph).
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.87,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最強を目指して 本気で作りこんでますわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:45.80,def2,....GOU....,0,0,0,,So there's a meaning to the\Nchoice of using the Eight-Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:44.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ハチロクという車種の選択にも意味があるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:47.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介の考えそうなことだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.86,def2,....GOU....,0,0,0,,That's something Ryosuke would come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:51.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,空力系のパーツを一切排除してるあたり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:54.70,def2,...KUBO....,0,0,0,,He knows what he's doing based on the fact that\Nthe car doesn't have any aerodynamic parts, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:54.01,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,間違いなく確信犯やね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:57.75,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,けど あのレベルになると
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:18:03.10,def2,...KUBO....,0,0,0,,...the level of competition is so high that the cars will momentarily\Nreach their critical speed even during the slow-speed stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:17:59.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら低速ステージでも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:03.43,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬間的には途方もない速度に達しますよって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:09.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サーキット走行でなければ効かないと言われてるGTウイングも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:12.44,def2,...KUBO....,0,0,0,,People say the GT wing only works on the circuit,\Nbut at their level, it's no longer a decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:12.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのレベルになれば ただの飾りじゃおまへん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:16.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負の分岐点は空力かもしれまへんな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:16.61,def2,...KUBO....,0,0,0,,Aerodynamics might decide\Nthe outcome of this race.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マツダの後輪駆動は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:32.22,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,Basically, Mazda's rear-wheel drive cars are designed\Nto have the roll axis a little forward of the mid-point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:31.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,基本的にロール軸は前下がりに設計されているのが特徴なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:40.05,def2,.MATSUMOTO.,0,0,0,,The FD is no exception, but the Roadster in particular gives you\Na better handling feel thanks to the biased load to the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:33.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,FDも同様ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:37.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,特にロードスターはフロント荷重で舵の効きをよくして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:40.26,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ハンドリングに軽快感を出してますからね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど攻め込んでいけば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:46.76,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,But if you push it harder, it tends to over-steer\Nbecause of the lack of load to the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:45.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,リアの荷重不足でオーバーステアが出てくる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ロードスターをチューニングしていくうえでは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:51.01,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,It becomes an unavoidable\Nissue when tuning a Roadster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それが一つのテーマになる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やり方は色々あるだろうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:19:03.19,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,There are many different approaches, but you can't\Neliminate the car's natural over-steering tendency.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:03.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,基本的に素性としてオーバーステア出易い点は変えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:06.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのあたりどういう処理をしているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.52,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,I wonder how they dealt with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ダウンヒルでオーバーステアはまずいよな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:10.33,def2,.FUMIHIRO..,0,0,0,,Over-steering on the downhill is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:13.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,むしろアンダーステアのほうがはるかに速く走れる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:14.12,def2,.FUMIHIRO..,0,0,0,,Instead, you can drive faster by under-steering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれだけの相手だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:18.44,def2,.FUMIHIRO..,0,0,0,,{aredake}Knowing our opponents, their car\Nmust have been perfectly tuned, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.61,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,車は完璧に仕上がってると思うが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:31.79,def2,.FUMIHIRO..,0,0,0,,If something destroys that balance,\NFujiwara will have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:28.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何かの拍子にバランスが崩れるようなことがあれば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:32.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,藤原にとってはチャンスなんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,追いつかね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:41.20,def2,..TAKUMI...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I can't catch him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:41.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,けど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:46.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,差が広がってもいなり
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:50.12,def2,..TAKUMI...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...the gap hasn't widened, even though\NI'm only tracing his car's line and speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:49.98,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,前の車のラインとスピードをトレースしてるだけなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまで走れるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:56.85,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's almost a miracle that you've kept up with me.{this far.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ある意味奇跡だな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:00.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここから先バックミラーは用なしだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:20:00.86,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}From this point on,\NI don't need the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで来れば もう駆け引きもない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:05.40,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{kokomade}No need to play a guessing game. I just\Nhave to look ahead and keep pushing hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:05.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ただひたすら前を向いて攻めるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろを気にするのはゴールに飛び込んでから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:09.90,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'll just have to check the\Nrear after crossing the goal line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとき俺は勝っている
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:11.57,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That's when I'll ensure my victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:27.30,def2,....MAN....,0,0,0,,The Eight-Six's headlights went off !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,消えた ハチロクのヘッドライトが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:30.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃねえぞ この真っ黒な峠道で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:32.71,def2,....MAN....,0,0,0,,No way ! On this pitch-black\Nmountain pass ? What's going on ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:32.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何が起こってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.61,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ハチロクのヘッドライトが消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:41.08,def2,.FUMIHIRO..,0,0,0,,The Eight-Six's headlights are off ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:42.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブラインドアタックか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:42.36,def2,.FUMIHIRO..,0,0,0,,The blind attack, huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.77,def2,.MATSUMOTO.,0,0,0,,Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:44.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:49.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく藤原ここまでの競り合いで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:54.00,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,During the race until now, Fujiwara must have intuitively\Nlearned that he's at a disadvantage in the high-speed sections.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:53.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,高速区間では不利なことを感覚的に察したんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,藤原独特の天恵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:56.99,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,Fujiwara's god sent talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:21:00.96,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,No, he may have heard\Nthe voice of the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:21:01.18,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいや　ハチロクの声を聞いたのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:06.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブラインドアタック
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:14.51,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,Blind attack, which is Fujiwara's forte, is a two-sided\Ndiversion technique of confusing his opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:09.50,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,藤原が得意とするこの技は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:14.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相手を動揺させると同時に攻撃ルートを悟らせないという
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:16.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二重の効果を狙った陽動作戦だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:17.50,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,...as well as hiding his offensive strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:22.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だがコースを熟知し なおかつ相手が異常に集中している時は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:23.00,def2,.FUMIHIRO..,0,0,0,,But when the opponent is familiar with\Nthe course and remains highly focused...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:27.28,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　狙ったはずの効果は生み出されない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:28.50,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,Right. It doesn't create the desired effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:29.58,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.28,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:35.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,リトラクタブルのヘッドライトは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:40.41,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,Retractable headlights have a lower drag\Ncoefficient value when they're lowered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:37.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,上げた状態よりも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:39.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,下げたほうがCD値が下がる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:42.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,空気抵抗が少なくなりますからね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:43.00,def2,.MATSUMOTO.,0,0,0,,Because of less air resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:48.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わずかながらも空気抵抗を減らすことにより
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:54.14,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,Fujiwara must have wanted to raise his top speed by\Nreducing the drag, even if only by a very small amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:50.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,トップスピードを稼ぎたいという気持ちが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:52.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,藤原にそれをさせたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:56.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,執念か 藤原の
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:56.40,def2,.FUMIHIRO..,0,0,0,,Fujiwara's tenacity ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その執念が突破口を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:22:03.21,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,His tenacity might create...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,開くことになるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:05.36,def2,..RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,...a breakthrough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:13.35,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブレーキングを開始するほんのわずかに手前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:13.35,def2,..TAKUMI...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Just before his braking action...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:15.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よく分かねえけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:17.00,def2,..TAKUMI...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm not exactly sure, but most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:18.87,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,たぶん ここだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:18.90,def2,..TAKUMI...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.69,0:22:42.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,速かった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:44.01,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It was too soon, if only by a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:43.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんの少し
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:49.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一体何が起こった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:49.30,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What the hell happened ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:55.21,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ 負けっかよ ここまで来て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:55.12,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Dammit, I won't lose after coming this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:01.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のスペースはきっちりもらうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:03.61,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'll keep my space.\NCan you keep up ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:03.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,着いて来れっかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:28.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ウイングをやっちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:31.77,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I messed up the wing.\NI've gotta keep the race short.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:31.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これは長びかせるわけにはいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.87,0:23:35.39,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一本目で 絶対に終わらせるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:35.38,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'll settle this match on the first run.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:46.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,車が妙なふらつき方をする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:47.40,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The car is unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:49.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ウイングがどうなってるのか知らないが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:51.66,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I don't know what's wrong with the wing,\Nbut the car's lateral balance is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:51.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,左右のバランスがおかしいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.06,0:23:57.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いっそのことちぎれて吹っ飛んでくれたほうがましだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:57.70,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I would've been better off if \Nit had broken off completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:04.86,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ　言い訳はしないぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.61,0:24:07.55,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Damn, no need for excuses. I just have\Nto motivate myself to raise my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.56,0:24:07.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気合で限界を上げりゃいい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.16,0:25:03.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は俺の日じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.30,0:25:05.52,def2,...OMIYA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}So, today wasn't my day after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.27,0:25:05.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なかったってことか
