Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.43,0:25:52.40,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Tayori ni naru mono wa sore shika mienakatta}The light was all I could depend on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.47,0:25:52.43,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,頼りになるものはそれしか見えなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.13,0:25:58.21,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,この並木道を抜けていけばきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.15,0:25:58.23,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Kono namiki michi wo nukete ikeba kitto}I felt like I could catch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.23,0:26:01.76,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Tsukameru youna ki ga shita}...if I passed through this tree-lined street.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.27,0:26:01.68,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,つかめるような気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.73,0:26:05.29,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,Give up! I just can't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.76,0:26:05.40,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Get up! I just can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.40,0:26:11.85,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Sokoniwa mada sagashimono wa nani mo nakute}I couldn't find what I'd been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.47,0:26:11.86,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,外にはまだ捜し物は何もなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.85,0:26:15.34,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Yeah, it starts at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.95,0:26:15.18,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It stops at this moment
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.34,0:26:19.01,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Kono basho kara}At this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.36,0:26:18.01,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,この場所から
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.01,0:26:22.39,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Please turn over the flyleaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.05,0:26:22.38,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,Please stand alone on the flyleaf
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.63,0:26:32.24,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,I lost my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.66,0:26:32.07,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,I lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.20,0:26:38.06,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,白く曇った窓と的外れなNavigation
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.24,0:26:35.30,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Shiroku kumotta mado to}Fogged up windows, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.30,0:26:38.64,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Mato hazure na navigation}...messed up navigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.59,0:26:41.95,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,赤く変わった信号で
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.64,0:26:42.30,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Akaku kawatta shingou de}As the stoplight turns red...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.11,0:26:48.28,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,サイドミラーに映る視界を遮るLight
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.30,0:26:48.97,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Side mirror ni utsuru shikai wo saegiru light}...a light in the side mirror blinds my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.88,0:26:53.85,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,冷たい風が入り込まないように
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.97,0:26:54.01,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Tsumetai kaze ga hairikomanai youni}I gradually close the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.99,0:26:57.35,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,窓をそっと締めたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.01,0:26:57.44,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Mado wo sotto shimetanda}...to stop the cold wind from blowing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.44,0:27:01.18,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Get up! I just can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.50,0:27:00.91,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,Give up! I just can't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.02,0:27:07.59,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに広がる道を選んで進む僕は
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.18,0:27:07.55,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Soko ni hirogaru michi wo erande susumu bokuwa}We must choose one of the paths that lie ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.55,0:27:10.97,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Yeah, it starts at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.66,0:27:10.89,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It stops at this moment
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.97,0:27:14.59,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,{Kimi ga iru nana}Because you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.98,0:27:13.73,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,君がいるなら
